{
  "chapter": 71,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十一回 情不断。萧风自诩能破解煞手三招，借此与张玉珍套上师门关系，将她放走。芮玮出面阻拦，揭露张玉珍三日前杀害高将军侧室及全府三十二条人命的罪行，但萧风偏袒同门，不听分辨。芮玮与萧风对峙，萧风狂妄自大，以先天掌让芮玮百招后反攻，招招要打芮玮耳光。芮玮宁死不受辱，拼死护脸。关键时刻，高莫静赶到舍身代受萧风致命一掌，却因身怀四照神功安然无恙。高莫静掌掴萧风，以四照神功震慑全场，萧风愤然离去，众侍卫亦纷纷辞退。事后芮玮向高寿忏悔伯母之死，高寿取出高莫野托官府送来的檀木长盒，盒中藏有海渊剑谱和一束青丝，象征高莫野对芮玮的情意不断。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "好说，好说，不错，那煞手三招虽是威力无比，萧某却有解救的对招，可是，我也不会伤你，我既认出你的掌法来历，要知煞手三招是本门师叔独创的武功，你我师门上定有渊源，我岂会贸然伤你，不怕家师叔的责怪？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么！那传我三招的独眼人是你师叔？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你学了我师叔的独创绝招还不知他的来历吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他只传我三招，别的什么话也没说，连个姓也没告诉我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我师叔的行径孤陋怪异，旁人想他煞手三招势难登天，我曾求他教我，他都不肯，你真有缘，能得他老人家欢心。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你师叔看得起我传我三招，我与你师叔不过数面之交，他就如此慷慨，哪会不传给阁下呢，我想令师叔认为煞手三招给阁下并无多大用处，所以不传，以阁下的武功何患会不会那煞手三招？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你的话有道理，本门武学博大精深，煞手三招虽是师叔独创的武功，本门武学中算不得奇特之学，师叔怕我本门功夫都学不完，何必多学煞手三招，可是，你能学到师叔的武功，总算有缘，称得上本门弟子了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这么说我称你师兄了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你既是师叔的半个徒弟，这声师兄生受了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "text": "诸位兄弟，此人前来行凶，定然是某种误会，现在弄清楚了，原来是萧某的同门，现在萧某自做主张，放她离开，将军那儿有我担当，你们要是不服，向我问话。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你去吧！这儿一切有我做主，见到师叔就说家师拳剑无双想他老人家，希他能回西藏一晤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "多谢师兄，我去了——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "留步！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可是叫我留步？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你既来此，得向高将军说个公道！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么公道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "三日前，高将军侧室，全府三十二条性命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么！她就是杀二夫人的凶手？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放不得！放不得……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快请将军来办这凶手……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢动！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要命的别动！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你没听我放她走吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "阁下受聘将军府，目的何在？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "保护将军性命，现在将军平安，我自有权放她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她杀了将军侧室，你不问问？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有杀，她不是凶手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "阁下怎知她不是凶手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你与她有没有仇？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有，仇恨很深。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这就明白了，你，姓芮的，假公济私，含血喷人，言词不足信。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你快走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "胆敢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "怎么？你敢和我动手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是高伯父的侍卫，我不跟你敌对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "撇下这关系，你看怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，犯不上动手成敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "懦夫！早知如此，谅你不敢去追本门弟子，虚张声势，嘿嘿！不错，正是虚张声势。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芮公子再给他一掌。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "懦夫！什么懦夫？人家是不屑与你争斗！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芮公子要得，饶了他吧，饶了他有天……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有何贵干？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "萧某要会会你，教那些有目无珠的人看看谁个厉害！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "在下自承不如，阁下可以不必生气了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说丁老三，功力不如人家最好别找人家麻烦。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找麻烦？人家不找他麻烦就好哕！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芮公子多谦逊啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_shi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "众侍卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真有功夫的人谁不谦逊，空架子的人才自命不凡。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我要好好会会你，不斗不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不同你斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我让你一百招，再不敢斗，你就是懦夫！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，我倒要见识见识你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "比掌还是比剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "随便，掌剑皆都奉陪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是将军故友之子，又是素心的好朋友，咱们不伤和气，比掌吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "素心？你说的素心指谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你管她是谁？放心，看她分上我不会伤你呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可惜一副好身手，却是银样腊枪头！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "打右耳光！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你再拼死守下去，萧某不客气了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好家伙，看你要命还是要脸！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好家伙，我一掌毙了你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "姐姐，姐姐，你……你……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你受了伤吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我……我……没……没……受伤……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那我就安心了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么要杀他？你不知道他是我爹爹故友之子吗？你安着什么歹心随便杀人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我并非你爹爹请来的侍卫，别用小姐口气来问我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的！今天有娘们庇护你，哪天没有庇护你时，萧某不打你一百下耳光，萧字永远倒过来写！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你凭什么资格要打他耳光？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "老子要打，谁管得着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想打别人耳光，今天先尝尝耳光的滋味。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你有本领再打我一掌！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，刚才左耳光，现在右耳光。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你既知道吃耳光的痛苦，那么该晓得当你打别人时，别人的痛苦了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "高小姐，我服你，但你不应偏袒姓芮的，令我难堪。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你这话什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "高伯父！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "静儿，这位大哥是你二妹的朋友，他义务前来保护你爹，野儿曾对为父言，咱们要好好礼待他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "好好礼待！你高伯父对我确实不错，但是高小姐，你的耳光之礼，我永远难忘啊！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你有本领保护我爹，就没有本领躲过吃耳光吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "算我萧某人多事，不自量力的应允素心之托，高伯父，你既有这么个女儿，也用不着萧某人吃口闲饭啦，我回去跟素心说，这里再不需要我啦。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
      "text": "慢走，你这么一走，野儿将来问我，教伯父如何说呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "爹，让他走，二妹多事，请他来做么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧风",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "青山永在，绿水长流，高小姐一记耳光，我萧某人永远记着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "走就走罢，爹的侍卫中多你这人，并无多大用处。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这些经过我都知道，未想到野儿师父杀我妻子，想当年张玉珍前来收野儿为徒时，尼姑装束，满面正派的样子，谁知是个杀人不眨眼的女魔！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "伯母之死，芮玮之罪。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "起来，起来，你何罪之有，快起来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "莫野妹为我盗张玉珍剑谱，张玉珍杀伯母，因莫野妹背叛之故，而莫野妹因我背叛，伯母之死，非芮玮之罪，何人之罪！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快别再说这种话，依此说，野儿出家为尼，又是你的罪过了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "莫野妹看破红尘，正是芮玮不仁不义之罪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "笑话，这也是罪，那也是罪，为人在世，罪过未免太多了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "伯父可真有莫野妹的消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你问起，我倒想起一件东西没有交给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "什么东西，谁给我的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你等着，我去拿来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这是野儿给你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "野儿！她……她在哪里？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你问我野儿消息，我亦不知，自凶杀案发生后，野儿再未见我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "那些物何来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不知野儿为何不再见我，这檀木盒，她托官府送来！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 71,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    }
